test_presence_of_duplicates_in_result:
assert (0 == 3)
 +  where 0 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x7bd4865368c0>([-15])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x7bd4865368c0> = [[1, -15], [1, -15, 1], [-15, 1], [-15, 1, -15], [1, -15], [1, -15, 1], ...].count
test_if_sublist_product_equals_number:
assert -75 == -15
 +  where -75 = <built-in function prod>([-5, -15, -1])
 +    where <built-in function prod> = math.prod
